msgctxt "156_Akiyama"
msgid "Sorry, mind if I ask you a question? Did you see any yakuza-looking guys around here?"
msgstr "Lo siento, ¿le importa si le hago una pregunta? ¿Vio a unos hombres con aspecto de yakuzas por aquí?"

msgctxt "168_Businessman"
msgid "Oh, all the time. This is Kamurocho we're talking about here. Why, did something happen?"
msgstr "Ah, todo el tiempo. Estamos en Kamurocho. ¿Por qué, pasó algo?"

msgctxt "180_Akiyama"
msgid "Yeah, they nabbed a friend of mine."
msgstr "Sí, secuestraron a un amigo mío."

msgctxt "192_Businessman"
msgid "What!? That's terrible!"
msgstr "¡¿Qué?! ¡Eso es terrible!"

msgctxt "204_Businessman"
msgid "Now that you mention it, I did see an especially conspicuous group pass by a few hours ago."
msgstr "Ahora que mencionas, hace unas horas vi pasar a un grupo que llamaba mucho la atención."

msgctxt "216_Akiyama"
msgid "What!?"
msgstr "¡¿Qué?!"

msgctxt "228_Businessman"
msgid "Definitely yakuza, by the look of them. They were dragging some poor guy behind them, too. Pretty roughed up."
msgstr "Por la apariencia definitivamente eran yakuzas. También arrastraban a un pobre hombre. Bastante maltratado."

msgctxt "240_Akiyama"
msgid "Where did they go?"
msgstr "¿A dónde fueron?"

msgctxt "252_Businessman"
msgid "Past the lockers where the underground mall used to be."
msgstr "Por los casilleros donde está el centro comercial subterráneo."

msgctxt "264_Akiyama"
msgid "Okay, I'll go take a look. Thanks."
msgstr "Bueno, iré a echar un vistazo. Gracias."

msgctxt "288_Akiyama"
msgid "Yeah, they stole my account book."
msgstr "Sí, me robaron mi libro de clientes."

msgctxt "300_Businessman"
msgid "What!? That's terrible!"
msgstr "¡¿Qué?! ¡Eso es terrible!"

msgctxt "312_Businessman"
msgid "An account book is a company's lifeblood. That's what we say in my line of work, at least."
msgstr "El libro de clientes es el alma de una empresa. Eso es lo que decimos en mi línea de trabajo."

msgctxt "324_Akiyama"
msgid "Agreed. I can't run my business without it."
msgstr "Estoy de acuerdo. No puedo dirigir mi negocio sin él."

msgctxt "336_Businessman"
msgid "Those guys over there look like trouble... See them? The yakuza-looking brutes in the middle of the square?"
msgstr "Esos tipos de allá parecen problemáticos... ¿Los ves? ¿Los grandotes con aspecto de yakuza en medio de la plaza?"

msgctxt "348_Businessman"
msgid "They're definitely up to something. Kept going on about busting up some finance company."
msgstr "Definitivamente están tramando algo. No paraban de hablar de destrozar alguna entidad financiera."

msgctxt "360_Akiyama"
msgid "What?"
msgstr "¿Qué?"

msgctxt "372_Businessman"
msgid "Kind of suspicious, don't you think? Maybe you should go see what they're up to."
msgstr "Un poco sospechoso, ¿no crees? Tal vez deberías ir a ver qué están haciendo."

msgctxt "384_Akiyama"
msgid "Yeah, I'll do that. Thanks."
msgstr "Sí, lo haré. Gracias."

msgctxt "408_Businessman"
msgid "So you want to know about yakuza, huh? Why, did something happen?"
msgstr "Así que quieres saber sobre la yakuza, ¿eh? ¿Por qué, pasó algo?"

msgctxt "444_Akiyama"
msgid "Yeah, they've taken a friend of mine."
msgstr "Sí, secuestraron a un amigo mío."

msgctxt "456_Businessman"
msgid "Like I said before, I saw a group of real shady characters pass by a few hours ago."
msgstr "Como dije antes, hace unas horas vi pasar a un grupo de personas realmente sospechosas."

msgctxt "468_Businessman"
msgid "They were dragging a man along with them; the poor guy looked all beat up. He was taken down past the lockers where the underground mall used to be."
msgstr "Arrastraban a un hombre con ellos, el pobre hombre parecía apaleado. Fueron más allá de los casilleros donde solía estar el centro comercial subterráneo."

msgctxt "480_Akiyama"
msgid "All right. Thanks, I'll check it out."
msgstr "Muy bien. Gracias, iré a ver."

msgctxt "492_Akiyama"
msgid "Yeah, they stole my account book."
msgstr "Sí, me robaron mi libro de clientes."

msgctxt "504_Businessman"
msgid "It's like I said, those guys over there look pretty suspicious..."
msgstr "Es como dije, esos chicos de allí se ven bastante sospechosos..."

msgctxt "516_Businessman"
msgid "See them? That yakuza-looking bunch on the edge of the square."
msgstr "¿Los ves? Esos tipos con aspecto de yakuzas en la plaza."

msgctxt "528_Businessman"
msgid "Sketchy as all heck, right? Maybe you should go see what they're up to."
msgstr "Bastante sospechosos. Tal vez deberías ir a ver qué están haciendo."

msgctxt "540_Akiyama"
msgid "Yeah, I'll do that. Thanks."
msgstr "Sí, lo haré. Gracias."

msgctxt "564_Akiyama"
msgid "They took a friend of mine."
msgstr "Se llevaron a un amigo mío."

msgctxt "576_Akiyama"
msgid "They stole my account book."
msgstr "Me robaron mi libro de clientes."

